{"tid":2017673,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港］傑志舊將巴倫古素近況","createTime":"2020-05-15T08:05:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-16T05:20:44.000Z","uid":314560,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"783159e416a6e35f317596f30eab6e04c9759ec9","tid":2017673,"uid":314560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:05:18.000Z","msg":"透過身處海外的傑志舊將，分享當地的疫情狀況以及在封城下的訓練方法，他們亦透過此機會向身處香港的傑志球迷打氣，希望疫情過後能再次踏上球賽的舞台上。<br />\n<br />\n現年38歲的傑志舊將巴倫古素，現時效力西班牙第三級別聯賽球會，我們找來這位昔日「空中霸王」談談他的現況以及聯賽停擺後的訓練情況。<br />\n<br />\n#挺身抗疫從自己做起<br />\n#wearekitchee<br />\n#突破界限<br />\n#BeyondTheLimits<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E13uFu4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE13uFu4.png&h=f303a74f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n佢算唔算傑志近十年最強中鋒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />原來仲踢緊西班牙聯賽<br />\n唔知會唔會再返港超踢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c1196014c06fe76c20b8cc2e8c4a27b459b3e1f","tid":2017673,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"係咪踢東方個高佬？"},{"pid":"c361cdead601f707b501b92d047156264dd096a0","tid":2017673,"uid":314560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c1196014c06fe76c20b8cc2e8c4a27b459b3e1f","tid":2017673,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"係咪踢東方個高佬？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:08:19.000Z","msg":"唔向左走向右走係"},{"pid":"8f04c4550745997ff4a26eadaee647e37e2b3495","tid":2017673,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c361cdead601f707b501b92d047156264dd096a0","tid":2017673,"uid":314560,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2c1196014c06fe76c20b8cc2e8c4a27b459b3e1f","tid":2017673,"uid":242358,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-15T08:07:13.000Z","msg":"係咪踢東方個高佬？"},"citedBy":1,"reply